articles.title: Watch 9-Year-Old Belt Out a Tina Turner Classic on ‘America’s Got Talent’ - Billboard
articles.description: Pranysqa's powerful rendition of Tina Turner's "River Deep, Mountain High" left the judges and audience stunned.
articles.content:
